data.value: Operating Instructions: ----------------------------------- 1. Enter the Server IP\Name details + Login&&Password if need. 2. Click "Test Connection". 3. If you want to Check Week Passwords - Mark V. 4. If the test was successful - you will be allowed to run the script. 5. Fill in the field "Title For Report" - This will appear at the beginning of the report. 6. Click on "Run Script" and Wait (1-2 minutes tun time) 7. The end output is in XML form. You can save this on your computer. 8. If you want Naya experts to analyze your report and email you their recommendations - click on the button "Send Xml to Naya"
